----------------------------------------------------------------------

Application Configuration

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Note: For development, use the IP address of your computer, not 'localhost',

so the mobile emulator/physical device can reach the Docker container.

API_BASE_URL=http://[YOUR_LOCAL_IP_ADDRESS]:3000/api/v1
APP_VERSION=1.0.0

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Public Keys (Safe to include in compiled app, but use environment files locally)

----------------------------------------------------------------------

PAYMENT_GATEWAY_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_YOUR_SANDBOX_PUBLIC